        <mxCell id="sOLaZpKRdjkeHPjkyI0H-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional Requirement:&lt;br&gt;1. user should be able to login in our system&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;2.user shoul be able to buy a subscription&lt;br&gt;3. search for movies&lt;br&gt;4.play the movie he want&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Non-Funtional Requirements&lt;br&gt;1. system should be scalable(millions of request per sec)&lt;br&gt;2. latency should be less while searching as well as while watching video&lt;br&gt;3. our system should be available evry time&lt;br&gt;availablity &amp;gt;&amp;gt; consisteny&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
